        <Parent_String>folk art (traditional art) [300056487], art genres [300056462], genres in the visual arts [300056444], concepts in the arts and humanities [300056107], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
